        "help": "<p>Write node for MCZ stoves. Sends commands to the MCZ Cloud API.</p><h3>Settings</h3><ul><li><b>Configuration</b>: The configuration node associated with the stove.</li></ul><h3>Input</h3><p>Two <code>msg.payload</code> formats are accepted:</p><ul><li><b>Object (recommended):</b> <code>{ \"command\": \"Power\", \"value\": 1 }</code>. The node builds the correct raw string automatically.</li><li><b>Raw string:</b> Pass the Socket.IO string directly (e.g. <code>C|WriteParametri|34|1</code>).</li></ul><h3>Output</h3><p>On every successful send, the node emits a confirmation message:</p><ul><li><code>msg.topic</code>: <code>mcz/SERIALNUMBER/command</code></li><li><code>msg.payload</code>: <code>{ command, value, raw }</code></li></ul>"
